os_list.name: UEFI for Rock 5B+
os_list.description: The Unified Extensible Firmware Interface (UEFI) is a specification for a software program that connects a computer's firmware to its operating system (OS).UEFI is expected to eventually replace the Basic Input/Output System (BIOS), but is compatible with it.
